        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks MT for information on <hi rend="italic">Drosera filiformis</hi> [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">8989</hi>].</p>  
<p>Warns her against publishing statement about <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi> bending towards flies or meat that they have not touched.</p>  
<p>Will send his book [<hi rend="italic">Insectivorous plants</hi>] when published.</p> 
        </abstract>
